CCNA Day 4 Assignment:

~~~
!@R4
conf t
 int e3/3
  ip add 208.8.8.11 255.255.255.0
  ip add 208.8.8.12 255.255.255.0 secondary
  no shut
  exit
 !
 int e0/1
  ip add 10.11.11.1 255.255.255.224
  no shut
 !
 int e0/3
  ip add 10.1.2.10 255.255.255.252
  no shut
 !
 ip route 0.0.0.0 0.0.0.0 208.8.8.2
 !
 router ospf 1
  router-id 4.4.4.4 
  network 4.4.4.4 0.0.0.0 area 0
  network 208.8.8.0 0.0.0.255 area 0
  network 10.11.11.0 0.0.0.31 area 0
  network 10.1.2.8  0.0.0.3 area 0
  network 10.1.1.8 0.0.0.3 area 0
  passive-interface e0/1
 end
~~~


~~~
!@R3
conf t
 int e0/3
  ip add 10.1.2.9 255.255.255.252
  no shut
 !
 int e0/1
  ip add 10.22.22.1 255.255.255.224
  no shut
 !
 router ospf 1
  router-id 3.3.3.3
  network 3.3.3.3 0.0.0.0 area 0
  network 10.1.2.8 0.0.0.3 area 0
  network 10.1.1.8 0.0.0.3 area 0
  network 10.22.22.0 0.0.0.31 area 0
  passive-interface e0/1
  end
~~~


~~~
!@P1
conf t
 hostname FINANCE
 int e0/1
  no shut
  ip add 10.11.11.11 255.255.255.224
  ip add 10.11.11.12 255.255.255.224 secondary
 !
 ip route 0.0.0.0 0.0.0.0 10.11.11.1
 end
~~~


~~~
!@P2
conf t
 hostname IT
 int e0/1
  no shut
  ip add 10.22.22.21 255.255.255.224
  ip add 10.22.22.22 255.255.255.224 secondary
 !
 ip route 0.0.0.0 0.0.0.0 10.22.22.1
 end
~~~




### Make R4 Vulnerable

~~~
!@R4
config t
 ip domain name R4.COM
 crypto key generate rsa modulus 2048
 ip ssh version 2
 username admin priv 15 secret pass
 line vty 0 4
  transport input all
  login local
  exit
 ip host www.bet11.com 208.8.8.11
 ip host www.bet12.com 208.8.8.12
 ip host www.bet100.com 208.8.8.100
 service finger
 service tcp-small-servers
 service udp-small-servers
 ip dns server
 ip http server
 ip http secure-server
 telephony-service
  no auto-reg-ephone
  max-ephones 5
  max-dn 20
  ip source-address 208.8.8.11 port 2000
  exit
 voice service voip
  allow-connections h323 to sip
          
  allow-connections sip to h323
  allow-connections sip to sip
  supplementary-service h450.12
 sip
   bind control source-interface e3/3
   bind media source-interface e3/3
   registrar server expires max 600 min 60
 voice register global
  mode cme
  source-address 208.8.8.11 port 5060 secondary 208.8.8.12
  max-dn 12
  max-pool 12
  authenticate register
  create profile sync syncinfo.xml
  end
~~~




### 1. Using a STANDARD ACL, prevent FINANCE from Remotely Accessing R4
- Make sure the STANDARD ACL uses the highest number identifier.



### 2. Create an ACL that will prevent FINANCE from
- Sending PINGs outside of FINANCE
- Prevent Accessing R3 via TELNET
- Allow only P1-12 (10.11.11.12) to PING R3 on its loopback interface
 


### 3. Modify the ACL on R4 without removing existing entries in the ACL, 
to allow IT to PING and TELNET FINANCE but not the otherway around.




### 4. Allow the Following Ports on R4's e3/3 interface
- www.bet11.com  : FTP, SIP, MySQL NTP
- www.bet12.com  : IMAPS, POP3S, SUBMISSION, SMTPS




### 5. Setup R4 as a Proxy for the ff:
- www.bet100.com : 80 & 8080
- www.bet100.com : 443 & 8443

